        <div class="fc-step-item"><span class="fc-step-number">2</span><span>I'LL SERVE IT TO YOU IN SECONDS...</span></div>
        <div class="fc-step-item"><span class="fc-step-number">3</span><span>DISCOVER YOUR NEW FAVORITE PERFUME AND ENJOY IT!</span></div>
      </div>
